Water Walk

An experienced druid may use this spell to gain the
protection of the ocean spirits, allowing him to
walk on the surface of water without drowning.  At
higher levels of mastery, the druid can impart this
ability to others.

Command: waterwalk <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 40 SP
Base Recovery: long
Base Effect: travel (over oceans)
Base Duration: long
Guild Level: 7
